INSTALL - Anteater Chess v1.0
Team: Hikaru Naka-more
Course: EECS 22L, UC Irvine, Spring 2026

=====================================================================
DEPENDENCIES
=====================================================================
- GCC compiler
- GTK+3.0 library (libgtk-3-dev)
- GNU Make

To install GTK+3.0 on Ubuntu/Debian:
    sudo apt-get install libgtk-3-dev

=====================================================================
SOURCE CODE INSTALLATION
=====================================================================
1. Extract the source package:
    tar -xvzf Chess_V1.0_src.tar.gz

2. Navigate to the directory:
    cd Chess_V1.0_src

3. Build the program:
    make

4. Run the program:
    ./bin/chess

5. To run tests:
    make test

6. To clean build files:
    make clean

=====================================================================
USER PACKAGE INSTALLATION
=====================================================================
1. Extract the user package:
    tar -xvzf Chess_V1.0.tar.gz

2. Navigate to the directory:
    cd Chess_V1.0

3. Run the program directly (no compilation needed):
    ./bin/chess

=====================================================================
For more details refer to doc/Chess_UserManual.pdf
=====================================================================